      • timeToReceiveDesiredResponse

        protected R timeToReceiveDesiredResponse​(java.time.Duration time)
        This method defines the time to get expected http response. It has sense when some Predicate that describes expected http response is set up via conditionToReceiveDesiredResponse(Predicate). This time is ignored otherwise.
